bilingual.target: 我找到了一盘旧的盒式磁带。

bilingual.source: He found an old tape in the attic.
bilingual.target: 他在阁楼里找到了一盘旧磁带。

bilingual.source: He used the rewinder to fix the cassette tape.
bilingual.target: 他用倒带器修复了磁带。

bilingual.source: The tape was damaged and couldn't be played.
bilingual.target: 这盘磁带损坏了，无法播放。

bilingual.source: She listened to the tape over and over again.
bilingual.target: 她一遍又一遍地听这盘磁带。

bilingual.source: I used a tape to record my favorite songs.
bilingual.target: 我用磁带录下了我最喜欢的歌曲。

bilingual.source: The rewinder helps to rewind the tape quickly.
bilingual.target: 倒带器可以帮助快速倒带磁带。

bilingual.source: The old tape contains many childhood memories.
bilingual.target: 这盘旧磁带包含了许多童年的回忆。

bilingual.source: This album was originally released on cassette tape.
bilingual.target: 这张专辑最初是以盒式磁带形式发行的。

yingyinNormal.en: Yondu! Do you have any tape? Gamora? You have the tape? Tape! Never mind. Drax? Do you have any tape?
yingyinNormal.zh: 喂，勇度。你有，嗷，你那儿有胶带吗？卡魔拉？你有胶带吗？胶带？算了没事儿。德拉克斯？你有胶带吗？

yingyinNormal.en: Nobody has any tape! Not a single person has tape? Nope.
yingyinNormal.zh: 没人有胶带！就没有一个人带着胶带吗？没。

yingyinNormal.en: Does anybody have any tape out there? I wanna put some tape over the death button. I don't have any tape. Let me check.
yingyinNormal.zh: 外面有谁带了胶带吗？我想把那个按钮粘上。我没有胶带。我去问问。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, my God. What? There's a tape here with Monica's name on it. A tape with a girl's name on it. It's probably a sex tape.
yingyinNormal.zh: 喔，我的天。怎么了？有一卷带子上面有莫妮卡的名字。有一卷带子上面有女生的名字 可能是性爱录影带。

yingyinNormal.en: Yeah, Scotch tape would work. Then why did you ask me if Scotch tape would work if you don't have any?
yingyinNormal.zh: 嗯，透明胶也可以。没有那你问我能不能用干什么？

yingyinNormal.en: Well, I did put a lot of thought in the tape.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我的确花了很多心血。

yingyinNormal.en: What am I gonna do now? Just pass the tape along.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我该怎么办啦？就给你上司看看咯！

yingyinNormal.en: I got it. Scotch tape. How did you know she would buy scotch tape? Well, we used there's up last night making scary faces.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我知道了胶带。你怎么知道她会买胶带？我们昨晚玩扮鬼脸时，把她们的胶带用光了。

yingyinNormal.en: But I made you a tape of what I think are all romantic songs.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我录了一卷浪漫情歌给你。

yingyinNormal.en: I told you to put tape on his mouth! And I told you he bit me!
yingyinNormal.zh: 我说了让你用胶带封住他的嘴！我也说了这货咬我！

yingyinNormal.en: No! Hey, you're making him nervous! Shut up and give me some tape!
yingyinNormal.zh: 不是!你这样他会更紧张的！闭嘴！给我找点胶带来！

yingyinNormal.en: What's that piece of tape? Oh, that one doesn't apply to you. You sit.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这条黄线又是干嘛的？你用不着担心这个，反正你坐着上厕所。

yingyinNormal.en: We know, he already did it last week. You can watch our tape if you want.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们知道，他上个礼拜就会了，你可以看我们的带子。

yingyinNormal.en: I need the bonding tape, hurry! What about you? I gotta get back to Jakku.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我需要发动机胶带，赶紧！你要去哪儿？我必须得回贾库星去。

yingyinNormal.en: You know what? It's not fair to her. Let's just forget the tape. Thank you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那对她来说不公平，忘了录影带的事吧。谢谢。

yingyinNormal.en: All right. Oh. Shoot. Oh shoot. Rachel wanted to see this tape. What is it?
yingyinNormal.zh: 快点，瑞秋想看这卷录影带。那是什么？

yingyinNormal.en: I'm sorry you guys missed it but I did tape it so if you guys want to see it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 很遗憾你们错过，但我录下来了，你们要看的话…

yingyinNormal.en: Just tell Joey that you watched the tape and you liked it, but your bosses didn't.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那就告诉乔伊，你看过带子，你很喜欢，但你的老板们不喜欢。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, I'd hardly call this kidnapping. Where's the blindfold? Where's the duct tape?
yingyinNormal.zh: 这算哪门子绑架，也没胶布封嘴，封嘴的胶布呢？

yingyinNormal.en: And to make it worse, they turned me into a cartoon and slapped tape across my mouth.
yingyinNormal.zh: 更可恶的是他们居然把我画成这样，在我的嘴上画胶带。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: It must take responsibility for the signal it sends women about the social <highlight>tape</highlight>-measure they must use to determine their individual worth.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 它必须为它向女性发出的信号负责，即她们必须用社会卷尺来衡量自己的个人价值。

examination_example.sentence_trans: 在香港，我见过女孩们用一种特殊的瘦身胶带包裹全身或双腿。

examination_example.sentence: Her time-lapse videos of the revivals look like someone playing a <highlight>tape</highlight> of the plant's death in reverse.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 她拍摄的复苏的延时视频看起来像是有人在倒放植物死亡的磁带。

examination_example.sentence: Therefore, it's hard for these parents to fight the urge to <highlight>tape</highlight> pillows around their kids.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 因此，对于这些父母来说，很难抑制用胶带把枕头粘在孩子身边的冲动。
